* Data Lineage in\nUnity Catalog
** What it captures
***_ Runtime lineage automatically
***_ All languages (SQL, Python, Scala)
***_ Column-level relationships
***_ Notebooks, jobs, dashboards
** Compute requirements
***_ Unity Catalog-enabled clusters
***_ SQL warehouses with UC enabled
***_ Jobs on UC-enabled clusters
** Scope
***_ Cross-workspace (same metastore)
***_ Retained for 1 year
** Not captured
***_ Non-UC clusters
***_ Path-based table access
***_ Global temp views
@endmindmap
